snippet.title: Space Mavericks - Official Trailer (2021)
snippet.description:
Space Mavericks is a multiplayer artillery action game that is recreating the classic artillery style of aiming and shooting by adjusting the angle and power. Get a spaceship, travel through galaxies and fight battles for your freedom! 

You can download Space Maverick's demo here:
Steam: https://bit.ly/3ooEgi7
Android: https://bit.ly/3eL3eoE
iOS: https://apple.co/33JexHJ

------------------------------------------
